{"type":"message","id":"557d8d7d","parentId":"73cd6966","timestamp":"2026-03-03T20:30:50.008Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在让我继续深入分析：\n\n1. 现有 cron 任务只有 3 个，且都是基础监控\n2. 有很多修复脚本未集成（6 个以上）\n3. 429 错误持续出现\n4. 子代理并发启动导致 429 激增（PAT-064）\n\n让我检查：\n1. 最近 12 小时的 session logs（看看具体的错误模式）\n2. 现有的 Skills 状态\n3. 是否有重复的工作流可以提炼\n\n然后我需要执行主动改进：\n- 可能需要创建一个新的 Skill 来管理子代理并发启动\n- 或者改进现有的 api-rate-limiter\n- 或者创建一个子代理延迟启动机制","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9a77b5c169ca4ce992a0f52a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw -name \"*.log\" -mmin -720 -type f 2>/dev/null | head -10","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3555f18ad4d340a59a9104ca","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -lth /root/.openclaw/logs/ 2>/dev/null | head -20","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4c3391ac985442b69e306562","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"429\" /root/.openclaw/logs/*.log 2>/dev/null | tail -30","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ab5d6e5beeb14cb294a554f2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/evolved-api-rate-limiter/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":5471,"output":310,"cacheRead":19456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772569835944}}
