{"type":"message","id":"41ae0015","parentId":"6d40a3ff","timestamp":"2026-03-03T20:31:21.114Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6c60b78eefca4839a6354944","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Cron 任务智能集成脚本\n# 创建时间: 2026-03-04\n# 创建方式: evolver-self-evolution (Round 270)\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"\nFIXES_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/evolver/fixes\"\nINTEGRATION_LOG=\"$WORKSPACE/logs/cron-integration.log\"\nINTEGRATION_STATE=\"$WORKSPACE/logs/cron-integration-state.json\"\n\n# 日志函数\nlog() {\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $1\" | tee -a \"$INTEGRATION_LOG\"\n}\n\n# 扫描未集成的工具\nscan_tools() {\n    log \"🔍 扫描 evolver/fixes/ 目录...\"\n    \n    local tools=(\n        \"api-health-checker.sh\"\n        \"api-rate-limiter.sh\"\n        \"memory-archiver.sh\"\n        \"threat-detector.sh\"\n        \"ip-blocker.sh\"\n        \"nginx-security-enhance.sh\"\n    )\n    \n    local found=0\n    local integrated=0\n    \n    for tool in \"${tools[@]}\"; do\n        local tool_path=\"$FIXES_DIR/$tool\"\n        \n        if [ -f \"$tool_path\" ]; then\n            ((found++))\n            \n            # 检查是否已集成到 cron\n            if crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -q \"$tool\"; then\n                log \"  ✅ $tool - 已集成\"\n                ((integrated++))\n            else\n                log \"  ⚠️  $tool - 未集成\"\n            fi\n        fi\n    done\n    \n    log \"📊 扫描结果: 发现 $found 个工具，已集成 $integrated 个\"\n    \n    return $((found - integrated))\n}\n\n# 集成工具到 cron\nintegrate_tools() {\n    log \"🔧 开始集成工具到 cron...\"\n    \n    # 定义要添加的 cron 任务\n    local cron_tasks=(\n        \"# API 健康检查（每小时）\"\n        \"0 * * * * $FIXES_DIR/api-health-checker.sh --check >> $WORKSPACE/logs/api-health.log 2>&1\"\n        \"\"\n        \"# API Rate Limit 自动调整（每小时）\"\n        \"0 * * * * $FIXES_DIR/api-rate-limiter.sh --auto-adjust >> $WORKSPACE/logs/rate-limit.log 2>&1\"\n        \"\"\n        \"# 威胁检测（每小时）\"\n        \"0 * * * * $FIXES_DIR/threat-detector.sh --check >> $WORKSPACE/logs/threats.log 2>&1\"\n        \"\"\n        \"# Memory 归档（每周日凌晨 2 点）\"\n        \"0 2 * * 0 $FIXES_DIR/memory-archiver.sh --archive 30 --force >> $WORKSPACE/logs/memory-archiver.log 2>&1\"\n    )\n    \n    # 备份当前 crontab\n    local backup_file=\"/tmp/crontab.backup.$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S)\"\n    crontab -l > \"$backup_file\" 2>/dev/null || true\n    log \"💾 Crontab 备份: $backup_file\"\n    \n    # 添加新任务\n    local added=0\n    for task in \"${cron_tasks[@]}\"; do\n        if [ -n \"$task\" ]; then\n            # 跳过注释行，只检查实际任务\n            if [[ \"$task\" != \\#* ]]; then\n                # 检查是否已存在\n                if ! crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -F \"$task\" > /dev/null; then\n                    echo \"$task\" | crontab -\n                    ((added++))\n                fi\n            fi\n        fi\n    done\n    \n    log \"✅ 添加了 $added 个新的 cron 任务\"\n    \n    # 显示当前 crontab\n    log \"📋 当前 crontab:\"\n    crontab -l | grep -v \"^$\" | while read line; do\n        log \"  $line\"\n    done\n\n[125 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772569881112}}
{"type":"message","id":"08a0b1af","parentId":"41ae0015","timestamp":"2026-03-03T20:31:40.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我有了足够的信息来进行分析和主动改进。让我总结一下发现的问题：\n\n### 发现的问题：\n\n1. **PAT-064: 子代理并发启动导致 429 限流激增**（严重）\n   - 从 session 日志看到，3个子代理同时启动后立即触发 429 错误\n   - 导致 2/3 的子代理失败\n   - 这是一个重复出现的模式\n\n2. **工具未集成**（中等）\n   - 6 个工具已创建但未集成到 cron\n   - cron-integration.sh 已经存在但未执行集成\n\n3. **MEMORY.md 过大**（中等）\n   - 4.7M，63073 行\n   - 归档脚本已创建但未执行\n\n4. **EvoMap 心跳错误**（新发现）\n   - \"Request path contains unescaped characters\" 持续出现\n   - 心跳日志有重复输出\n\n5. **429 Rate Limit 持续**（持续）\n   - 最近 6 小时 24+ 次\n   - 集中在 16:00-20:00 高峰期\n\n### 改进计划：\n\n我应该执行以下主动改进：\n\n**A. 创建新 Skill** - 子代理智能调度器\n- 目的：避免并发启动子代理导致 429\n- 功能：串行化或延迟启动子代理\n\n**B. 执行工具集成**\n- 运行 cron-integration.sh --integrate\n\n\n- 将 6 个工具集成到 cron\n\n**C. 执行 MEMORY.md 归档**\n- 运行 memory-archiver.sh\n- 减少 MEMORY.md 大小\n\n**D. 更新进化历史**\n- 记录本轮改进\n\n接下来我将生成详细的进化报告，追踪每个改进措施的实施情况和效果。我会仔细记录每个步骤的执行细节和潜在影响。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"基于深入分析，我发现了多个需要改进的问题。让我执行主动改进措施："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a7f0caaecdb64128b8965019","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"bash /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/cron-integration.sh --integrate 2>&1","timeout":30,"workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4df5cee58e0843f886a2edce","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"bash /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/memory-archiver.sh --archive 30 --force 2>&1 | head -50","timeout":60,"workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":11062,"output":529,"cacheRead":32640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44231,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772569881114}}
