{"type":"message","id":"646126d6","parentId":"f1ce9d38","timestamp":"2026-03-04T00:34:09.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"发现了几个重要问题：\n\n1. **API Health Checker 无法找到 API Key** - 这是一个严重问题，导致无法检测 API 健康\n2. **Threat Detector 脚本有 bug** - line 44 有整数表达式错误\n3. **内存资源紧张** - Gateway 占用 1.4 GB，系统可用内存仅 747 MB\n4. **Swap 未配置** - 0 B，无内存缓冲\n\n让我创建一个改进计划：\n\n**A. 创建新 Skill**: Gateway 内存优化\n**B. 改进现有 Skill**: 修复 threat-detector.sh 脚本\n**C. 生成修复脚本**: Swap 配置脚本\n**D. 更新进化历史**: 记录发现的问题\n\n让我先修复 threat-detector.sh 的 bug。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现了多个需要改进的问题。让我执行主动改进措施："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_846cd1c7f89d49efa1e69be5","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/threat-detector.sh","limit":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5a8069da678e4c5394b16d65","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/threat-detector.sh","oldText":"    # 检查阈值\n    if [ $scan_count -gt 5 ]; then\n        log \"🔴 严重威胁：检测到大量 $pattern 扫描\"\n        THREAT_LEVEL=\"critical\"\n    elif [ $scan_count -gt 2 ]; then\n        log \"🟡 中等威胁：检测到多次 $pattern 扫描\"\n        THREAT_LEVEL=\"high\"\n    elif [ $scan_count -gt 0 ]; then\n        log \"🟢 轻微威胁：检测到 $pattern 扫描\"\n        THREAT_LEVEL=\"medium\"\n    fi","newText":"    # 检查阈值（确保 scan_count 是有效数字）\n    scan_count=${scan_count:-0}\n    \n    if [ \"$scan_count\" -gt 5 ] 2>/dev/null; then\n        log \"🔴 严重威胁：检测到大量 $pattern 扫描\"\n        THREAT_LEVEL=\"critical\"\n    elif [ \"$scan_count\" -gt 2 ] 2>/dev/null; then\n        log \"🟡 中等威胁：检测到多次 $pattern 扫描\"\n        THREAT_LEVEL=\"high\"\n    elif [ \"$scan_count\" -gt 0 ] 2>/dev/null; then\n        log \"🟢 轻微威胁：检测到 $pattern 扫描\"\n        THREAT_LEVEL=\"medium\"\n    fi"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1349,"output":537,"cacheRead":92800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94686,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cach