\\\"tool\\\": \\\"edit\\\",\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"Could not find the exact text in /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-04.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\\"\\n}\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"error\":\"Could not find the exact text in /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-04.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1772597115591}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e473dd17\",\"parentId\":\"e764c181\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T04:05:36.975Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"我需要直接写入完整的更新后的日志文件。让我先读取当前内容。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_ae6be628ee2e467ab9ebea4e\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"path\":\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-04.md\",\"limit\":100,\"offset\":1}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"zai\",\"model\":\"glm-5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":1206,\"output\":53,\"cacheRead\":134784,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":136043,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1772597115598}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"ac9bbc7e\",\"parentId\":\"e473dd17\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T04:05:36.981Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_ae6be628ee2e467ab9ebea4e\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# 2026-03-04 工作记录\\n\\n## 定时任务：OpenClaw 仓库更新分析\\n\\n### 📊 版本概览\\n\\n- **当前最新版本**: v1.23.0 (2026-03-03 12:44 UTC)\\n- **本地版本**: v1.20.3\\n- **更新范围**: v1.20.3 → v1.23.0 (37 个新提交)\\n- **更新时间跨度**: 约 2 周\\n\\n### 🆕 核心新功能（v1.22.0 - v1.23.0）\\n\\n#### 1. LLM 代码审查机制 (llmReview.js)\\n- **功能**: 在代码变更应用前进行 LLM 审查\\n- **启用**: 设置环境变量 `EVOLVER_LLM_REVIEW=true`\\n- **审查标准**:\\n  - 变更是否解决了目标信号\\n  - 是否引入了回退或 bug\\n  - 爆炸半径是否合理\\n  - 安全和稳定性考虑\\n- **输出**: JSON 格式的审查结果（approved, confidence, concerns, summary）\\n\\n#### 2. 进化叙事记忆 (narrativeMemory.js)\\n- **功能**: 按时间顺序记录进化决策和结果\\n- **存储**: `{evolution_dir}/narrative.md`\\n- **记录内容**:\\n  - 时间戳、基因 ID、分类\\n  - 信号列表、分数、影响范围\\n  - 变更理由、策略、结果摘要\\n- **限制**: 最多保留 30 条记录，总大小 12KB\\n\\n#### 3. 战略反思机制 (reflection.js)\\n- **功能**: 定期分析进化模式并提供战略指导\\n- **触发**: 每 5 个周期 + 冷却时间 30 分钟\\n- **分析内容**:\\n  - 最近 10 次周期的成功/失败统计\\n  - 意图分布、基因使用频率\\n  - 当前信号、记忆建议\\n- **输出**: 战略建议文件\\n\\n#### 4. 资产调用日志 (assetCallLog.js)\\n- **功能**: 追踪与 Hub 的资产交互\\n- **存储**: `{evolution_dir}/asset_call_log.jsonl` (追加式日志)\\n- **追踪类型**:\\n  - `hub_search_hit` / `hub_search_miss` - 搜索结果\\n  - `asset_reuse` - 资产复用\\n  - `asset_reference` - 资产引用\\n  - `asset_publish` / `asset_publish_skip` - 发布事件\\n- **CLI 支持**: `evolver asset-log [--run=ID] [--action=TYPE] [--last=N]`\\n\\n### 🔧 重要改进\\n\\n#### Hub 搜索优化\\n- **协议升级**: 使用 POST `/a2a/fetch` 替代 GET `/a2a/assets/search`\\n  - 单次往返获取完整 payload（content, diff, strategy）\\n  - 协议原生支持，更可靠\\n- **评分算法改进**:\\n  ```javascript\\n  // 旧: rank = confidence * max(success_streak, 1) * (reputation / 100)\\n  // 新: rank = confidence * min(max(success_streak, 1), 5) * (reputation / 100)\\n  ```\\n  - 添加 `MAX_STREAK_CAP = 5` 防止分数无限膨胀\\n  - 修复 reputation 默认值处理（`Number.isFinite` 检查）\\n\\n#### 进程管理改进\\n- **单例锁机制**:\\n  - 添加 PID 有效性检查（`Number.isFinite(pid) && pid > 0`）\\n  - 修复损坏锁文件导致的误判\\n- **进程重启**:\\n  - 调整 spawn 和 releaseLock 顺序\\n  - 添加 spawn 失败处理，继续当前进程而不是崩溃\\n\\n#### 路径管理改进\\n- **solidify 状态路径**: 使用 `getEvolutionDir()` 而非硬编码 `memory/` 目录\\n- **一致性**: 所有进化相关文件统一存储在配置的 evolution 目录\\n\\n### 🤝 社区贡献（已合并 PR）\\n\\n#### PR #21 - .env 加载路径修复 (LKCY33)\\n- **问题**: `../../.env` 路径在自定义目录运行时报 ENOENT\\n- **修复**: 改为 `./.env` (当前目录)\\n- **新增**: `.env.example` 配置示例\\n\\n#### PR #63 - 单元测试 (voidborne-d)\\n- **内容**: 为核心 GEP 模块添加单元测试\\n- **注释**: 添加 `clamp01(Infinity)` 行为说明\\n\\n#### PR #68 - dry-run 模式修复 (hendrixAIDev)\\n- **问题**: `performMaintenance()` 在 dry-run 模式下仍会移动/删除文件\\n- **影响**: 意外移动 1000+ 会话日志文件\\n- **修复**: 添加 `IS_DRY_RUN` 检查，确保只读模式\\n\\n#### PR #25 - Bug 批量修复 (onthebigtree/Yewlne)\\n1. **max_files 约束被忽略**:\\n   - `Math.max(Number(constraints.max_files) || 0, 20)` 强制最小值 20\\n   - 修复: 使用条件判断，未配置时才使用默认值\\n2. **变量遮蔽问题**:\\n   - `solidify.js` 和 `evolve.js` 中重复声明变量\\n   - 移除内部重复声明，使用外部作用域\\n\\n[68 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1772597136977}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"c1af251c\",\"parentId\":\"ac9bbc7e\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T04:05:41.318Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"zai\",\"model\":\"glm-5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":0,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"error\",\"timestamp\":1772597136981,\"errorMessage\":\"400 API 调用参数有误，请检查文档。Request 137259 input tokens exceeds the model's maximum context length 202752\"}}\n{\"type\":\"compaction\",\"id\":\"72267b08\",\"parentId\":\"c1af251c\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T04:08:44.505Z\",\"summary\":\"## Goal\\n- Execute automated system self-evolution tasks (evolver-self-evolution cron)\\n- Perform deep log analysis on session logs from `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl` for last 6-12 hours\\n- Run automated novel review system (novel-auto-review cron)\\n- Monitor and improve system health through pattern recognition and skill creation\\n- Generate reports to `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/` and update evolution-history\\n\\n## Constraints & Preferences\\n- Analyze last **6-12 hours** of logs (not just recent 30 minutes)\\n- Focus on: errors, warnings, timeout, API failures, resource anomalies\\n- Output format: P0/P1/P2/P3 severity levels for issues\\n- Do NOT just say \\\"system stable\\\" - actively dig for potential problems\\n- Must update pattern registry when new issues discovered\\n- Must create/modify skills and scripts to address identified problems\\n\\n## Progress\\n### Done\\n- [x] Round 267: Created `evolved-memory-archiver` skill and `api-health-checker.sh` script\\n- [x] Round 271: Deep log analysis completed with full report\\n- [x] Identified 7 session log files from 2026-03-03 22:00 to 2026-03-04 04:00\\n- [x] Identified error patterns:\\n  - **P0**: API 401 authentication failures (613 occurrences, now recovered)\\n  - **P1**: 429 rate limit errors (ongoing)\\n  - **P2**: Multiple cron tasks in error status\\n  - **P2**: Malicious IP 45.156.87.205 scanning .env files\\n  - **P2**: MEMORY.md oversized (4.7 MB, 63074 lines)\\n- [x] Novel reviews (Rounds 69-72): Reviewed chapters 9-10, 1-60, 11, 12\\n- [x] Generated log analysis report: `memory/log-analysis-2026-03-04-0400.md`\\n- [x] Created daily work log: `memory/2026-03-04.md`\\n- [x] Updated pattern registry with PAT-059 through PAT-064\\n\\n### In Progress\\n- [ ] Implementing subagent serialization to reduce 429 rate limit errors\\n- [ ] Configuring Swap space (currently 0B)\\n- [ ] Optimizing cron task scheduling to avoid concurrent API calls\\n\\n### Blocked\\n- Subagent tasks frequently failing due to API 429 rate limits (50% failure rate)\\n- Multiple novel review subagents (设定管理员, 人物分析师, 伏笔管理员, etc.) failed due to rate limiting\\n- Malicious IP blocking requires elevated permissions (iptables)\\n\\n## Key Decisions\\n- **API Recovery**: System switched to GLM-5 model via zai provider, API now functional\\n- **Created memory archiver skill**: MEMORY.md was 4.8MB, needed automatic archival mechanism\\n- **Created API health checker**: 401 errors went undetected for 16 hours before recovery\\n- **Added PAT-064 pattern**: Identified subagent concurrent startup causing 429 spike\\n- **Health score**: 6.5/10 based on API (7), Cron (6), Subagent (5), Resources (7), Interaction (9)\\n- **Security**: IP 45.156.87.205 identified as threat - needs manual blocking\\n\\n## Next Steps\\n1. Implement subagent serialization with 5-10 second delays between spawns\\n2. Configure 2GB Swap space for memory buffer\\n3. Optimize cron scheduling to stagger high-frequency tasks\\n4. Add API rate limit detection before spawning subagents\\n5. Continue monitoring 429 error frequency during peak hours (08:00-12:00, 16:00-20:00)\\n6. Block malicious IP 45.156.87.205 when elevated permissions available\\n\\n## Critical Context\\n- **API Status**: GLM-5 (zai provider) - 401 errors resolved, 429 rate limits persist\\n- **System Resources**: Memory 64% (599MB free), Disk 73% (14GB free), CPU 0.14 load, Swap 0B\\n- **Log files analyzed**: 7 files including SWE-Agent iterations, HEARTBEAT checks, autonomous exploration\\n- **Pattern Registry**: 62 active patterns, 47 resolved, 15 ongoing monitoring\\n- **Skills Count**: 37 skills, 33 fix scripts\\n- **Key Files**:\\n  - Evolution store: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/.cursor/evolution-store.json`\\n  - Pattern registry: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md`\\n  - Latest round: `round-271-20260304-0400.md`\\n  - Log analysis: `memory/log-analysis-2026-03-04-0400.md`\\n- **Error cron tasks**: evolver-self-evolution, swe-agent-iteration, novel-review-and-revise, 关系维护, analyze-openclaw-updates\\n- **Working cron tasks**: autonomous-exploration, evolver-log-analysis, nginx-security-daily\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\\n\\n## Goal\\nExecute deep log analysis task (cron: evolver-log-analysis) for the OpenClaw system:\\n- Analyze session logs from `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl` for the last 6 hours (02:00 - 08:00 on 2026-03-04)\\n- Identify error patterns, performance issues, API problems (401/403/429/500), configuration issues, and workflow problems\\n- Generate analysis report at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md`\\n- Update evolution history at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/`\\n- Update pattern-registry.md if new patterns discovered\\n\\n## Constraints & Preferences\\n- Must perform DEEP analysis, not lightweight check\\n- Proactively find potential issues even if no obvious errors\\n- Rank problems by severity (P0/P1/P2/P3)\\n- Provide specific fix recommendations\\n- Focus on: errors, warnings, timeouts, API failures, resource anomalies\\n\\n## Progress\\n### Done\\n- [x] Identified time range: 2026-03-04 02:00:32 to 08:00:32\\n- [x] Found 9 session files modified in last 6 hours\\n- [x] Checked system resources: Memory 2.7GB/3.6GB (used/total), Disk 73%, Load 0.12\\n- [x] Started error pattern analysis across session files\\n\\n### In Progress\\n- [ ] Completing error pattern extraction from all 9 session files\\n- [ ] Generating comprehensive analysis report\\n\\n### Blocked\\n- (none)\\n\\n## Key Decisions\\n- **Analysis window**: 6 hours back from 08:00 AM (02:00-08:00)\\n- **Files to analyze**: 9 jsonl files including `d0cb4348-49a4-4261-87b3-54c1cd72a258.jsonl` (largest at 756KB)\\n\\n## Next Steps\\n1. Complete error message extraction from remaining session files\\n2. Analyze stopReason patterns (toolUse/stop/error/aborted)\\n3. Check for API issues (401, 429 rate limits)\\n4. Identify subagent task failures (previous run showed 10 failed, 8 succeeded)\\n5. Generate report file at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-04-0800.md`\\n6. Update evolution history (Round 272)\\n7. Update pattern-registry.md if new patterns found\\n\\n## Critical Context\\n- **Previous analysis (04:00)** found: PAT-064 (subagent concurrent startup → 429 rate limit), 15x 401 errors (recovered), 24+ 429 errors, 12+ subagent failures\\n- **System state**: No swap configured, memory at 64% usage, disk at 73%\\n- **Active patterns**: 62 patterns tracked, health score 6.5/10\\n- **Key session files to analyze**:\\n  - `5bb4997f-9874-4e53-b8dc-6c463e16a15e.jsonl` - has 4x 401, 2x 429 errors\\n  - `1a2a2634-b3cc-40a1-b6a8-d1121b8cca51.jsonl` - has 4x 401 errors\\n  - `6c883048-65b7-4bd9-a492-6984cffddbc4.jsonl` - has 3x 429, 1x aborted, 1x 401\\n  - `d0c